<hr class="thin">
<STORY START><br />
<div class="su-row"><div class="su-column su-column-size-2-5"><div class="su-column-inner su-u-clearfix su-u-trim">
<a href="https://thewalrus.ca/in-cloud-country/"><img loading="lazy" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/Spot_Poetry-735x490.jpg" alt="" width="735" height="490" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-110841" /></a><br />
</div></div>
<div class="su-column su-column-size-3-5"><div class="su-column-inner su-u-clearfix su-u-trim">
<h3 style="font-family: GT Sectra; padding-bottom:0.2em; padding-top:0em; font-size:28px"><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/in-cloud-country/">In Cloud Country</a></h3>
<h6>BY MICHAEL PRIOR</h6>
<h5 style="font-family: GT Sectra; font-weight: 200;">Within our borders, / your hair frays cirrus into sky, while that bride, / so serious in every photo, never had to be you.</h5>
</div></div>
</div>
<STORY END></p>
