		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://thewalrus.ca/?p=156552</guid>

		`

		<description><![CDATA[Perched on / the tips of my fingers, they watch me with chest-puffed / caution or cap-tilted curiosity ]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="1200" height="800" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Poet_Tysdal2.jpg" class="webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image" alt="Photo of Daniel Scott Tysdal" loading="lazy" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;max-width: 100%;" link_thumbnail="" srcset="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Poet_Tysdal2.jpg 1200w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Poet_Tysdal2-735x490.jpg 735w, https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/SR23_Poet_Tysdal2-348x232.jpg 348w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><style>
